4843 Builtin::kReflectSetPrototypeOf, 2, kAdapt);
4844 }
4845
4846 { // --- B o u n d F u n c t i o n
4847 DirectHandle<Map> map = factory->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext(
4848 JS_BOUND_FUNCTION_TYPE, JSBoundFunction::kHeaderSize,
4849 TERMINAL_FAST_ELEMENTS_KIND, 0);
4850 map->SetConstructor(native_context()->object_function());
4851 map->set_is_callable(true);
4852 Map::SetPrototype(isolate(), map, empty_function);
4853
4854 PropertyAttributes roc_attribs =
4855 static_cast<PropertyAttributes>(DONT_ENUM | READ_ONLY);
4856 Map::EnsureDescriptorSlack(isolate_, map, 2);
4857
4858 { // length
4859 static_assert(
4860 JSFunctionOrBoundFunctionOrWrappedFunction::kLengthDescriptorIndex ==
4861 0);
4862 Descriptor d = Descriptor::AccessorConstant(
4863 factory->length_string(), factory->bound_function_length_accessor(),
4864 roc_attribs);
4865 map->AppendDescriptor(isolate(), &d);
4866 }
4867
4868 { // name
4869 static_assert(
4870 JSFunctionOrBoundFunctionOrWrappedFunction::kNameDescriptorIndex ==
4871 1);
4872 Descriptor d = Descriptor::AccessorConstant(
4873 factory->name_string(), factory->bound_function_name_accessor(),
4874 roc_attribs);
4875 map->AppendDescriptor(isolate(), &d);
4876 }
4877 native_context()->set_bound_function_without_constructor_map(*map);
4878
4879 map = Map::Copy(isolate_, map, "IsConstructor");
4880 map->set_is_constructor(true);
4881 native_context()->set_bound_function_with_constructor_map(*map);
4882 }
4883
4884 { // -- F i n a l i z a t i o n R e g i s t r y
4885 DirectHandle<JSFunction> finalization_registry_fun = InstallFunction(
4886 isolate_, global, factory->FinalizationRegistry_string(),
4887 JS_FINALIZATION_REGISTRY_TYPE, JSFinalizationRegistry::kHeaderSize, 0,
4888 factory->the_hole_value(), Builtin::kFinalizationRegistryConstructor, 1,
4889 kDontAdapt);
4890 InstallWithIntrinsicDefaultProto(
4891 isolate_, finalization_registry_fun,
4892 Context::JS_FINALIZATION_REGISTRY_FUNCTION_INDEX);
4893
4894 DirectHandle<JSObject> finalization_registry_prototype(
4895 Cast<JSObject>(finalization_registry_fun->instance_prototype()),
4896 isolate());
4897
4898 InstallToStringTag(isolate_, finalization_registry_prototype,
4899 factory->FinalizationRegistry_string());
4900
4901 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate_, finalization_registry_prototype, "register",
4902 Builtin::kFinalizationRegistryRegister, 2,
4903 kDontAdapt);
4904
4905 SimpleInstallFunction(
4906 isolate_, finalization_registry_prototype, "unregister",
4907 Builtin::kFinalizationRegistryUnregister, 1, kDontAdapt);
4908 }
4909
4910 { // -- W e a k R e f
4911 DirectHandle<JSFunction> weak_ref_fun =
4912 InstallFunction(isolate_, global, "WeakRef", JS_WEAK_REF_TYPE,
4913 JSWeakRef::kHeaderSize, 0, factory->the_hole_value(),
4914 Builtin::kWeakRefConstructor, 1, kDontAdapt);
4915 InstallWithIntrinsicDefaultProto(isolate_, weak_ref_fun,
4916 Context::JS_WEAK_REF_FUNCTION_INDEX);
4917
4918 DirectHandle<JSObject> weak_ref_prototype(
4919 Cast<JSObject>(weak_ref_fun->instance_prototype()), isolate());
4920
4921 InstallToStringTag(isolate_, weak_ref_prototype, factory->WeakRef_string());
4922
4923 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate_, weak_ref_prototype, "deref",
4924 Builtin::kWeakRefDeref, 0, kAdapt);
4925 }
4926
4927 { // --- sloppy arguments map
4928 DirectHandle<String> arguments_string = factory->Arguments_string();
4929 DirectHandle<JSFunction> function = CreateFunctionForBuiltinWithPrototype(
4930 isolate(), arguments_string, Builtin::kIllegal,
4931 isolate()->initial_object_prototype(), JS_ARGUMENTS_OBJECT_TYPE,
4932 JSSloppyArgumentsObject::kSize, 2, MUTABLE, 0, kDontAdapt);
4933 DirectHandle<Map> map(function->initial_map(), isolate());
4934
4935 // Create the descriptor array for the arguments object.
4936 Map::EnsureDescriptorSlack(isolate_, map, 2);
4937
4938 { // length
4939 Descriptor d =
4940 Descriptor::DataField(isolate(), factory->length_string(),
4941 JSSloppyArgumentsObject::kLengthIndex,
4942 DONT_ENUM, Representation::Tagged());
4943 map->AppendDescriptor(isolate(), &d);
4944 }
4945 { // callee
4946 Descriptor d =
4947 Descriptor::DataField(isolate(), factory->callee_string(),
4948 JSSloppyArgumentsObject::kCalleeIndex,
4949 DONT_ENUM, Representation::Tagged());
4950 map->AppendDescriptor(isolate(), &d);
4951 }
4952 // @@iterator method is added later.
4953
4954 native_context()->set_sloppy_arguments_map(*map);
4955
4956 DCHECK(!map->is_dictionary_map());
4957 DCHECK(IsObjectElementsKind(map->elements_kind()));
4958 }
4959
4960 { // --- fast and slow aliased arguments map
4961 DirectHandle<Map> map = isolate_->sloppy_arguments_map();
4962 map = Map::Copy(isolate_, map, "FastAliasedArguments");
4963 map->set_elements_kind(FAST_SLOPPY_ARGUMENTS_ELEMENTS);
4964 DCHECK_EQ(2, map->GetInObjectProperties());
4965 native_context()->set_fast_aliased_arguments_map(*map);
4966
4967 map = Map::Copy(isolate_, map, "SlowAliasedArguments");
4968 map->set_elements_kind(SLOW_SLOPPY_ARGUMENTS_ELEMENTS);
4969 DCHECK_EQ(2, map->GetInObjectProperties());
4970 native_context()->set_slow_aliased_arguments_map(*map);
4971 }
4972
4973 { // --- strict mode arguments map
4974 const PropertyAttributes attributes =
4975 static_cast<PropertyAttributes>(DONT_ENUM | DONT_DELETE | READ_ONLY);
4976
4977 // Create the ThrowTypeError function.
4978 DirectHandle<AccessorPair> callee = factory->NewAccessorPair();
4979
4980 DirectHandle<JSFunction> poison = GetThrowTypeErrorIntrinsic();
4981
4982 // Install the ThrowTypeError function.
4983 callee->set_getter(*poison);
4984 callee->set_setter(*poison);
4985
4986 // Create the map. Allocate one in-object field for length.
4987 DirectHandle<Map> map = factory->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext(
4988 JS_ARGUMENTS_OBJECT_TYPE, JSStrictArgumentsObject::kSize,
4989 PACKED_ELEMENTS, 1);
4990 // Create the descriptor array for the arguments object.
4991 Map::EnsureDescriptorSlack(isolate_, map, 2);
4992
4993 { // length
4994 Descriptor d =
4995 Descriptor::DataField(isolate(), factory->length_string(),
4996 JSStrictArgumentsObject::kLengthIndex,
4997 DONT_ENUM, Representation::Tagged());
4998 map->AppendDescriptor(isolate(), &d);
4999 }
5000 { // callee
5001 Descriptor d = Descriptor::AccessorConstant(factory->callee_string(),
5002 callee, attributes);
5003 map->AppendDescriptor(isolate(), &d);
5004 }
5005 // @@iterator method is added later.
5006
5007 DCHECK_EQ(native_context()->object_function()->prototype(),
5008 *isolate_->initial_object_prototype());
5009 Map::SetPrototype(isolate(), map, isolate_->initial_object_prototype());
5010
5011 // Copy constructor from the sloppy arguments boilerplate.
5012 map->SetConstructor(
5013 native_context()->sloppy_arguments_map()->GetConstructor());
5014
5015 native_context()->set_strict_arguments_map(*map);
5016
5017 DCHECK(!map->is_dictionary_map());
5018 DCHECK(IsObjectElementsKind(map->elements_kind()));
5019 }
5020
5021 { // --- context extension
5022 // Create a function for the context extension objects.
5023 DirectHandle<JSFunction> context_extension_fun = CreateFunction(
5024 isolate_, factory->empty_string(), JS_CONTEXT_EXTENSION_OBJECT_TYPE,
5025 JSObject::kHeaderSize, 0, factory->the_hole_value(), Builtin::kIllegal,
5026 0, kDontAdapt);
5027 native_context()->set_context_extension_function(*context_extension_fun);
5028 }
5029
5030 {
5031 // Set up the call-as-function delegate.
5032 DirectHandle<JSFunction> delegate = SimpleCreateFunction(
5033 isolate_, factory->empty_string(),
5034 Builtin::kHandleApiCallAsFunctionDelegate, 0, kDontAdapt);
5035 native_context()->set_call_as_function_delegate(*delegate);
5036 }
5037
5038 {
5039 // Set up the call-as-constructor delegate.
5040 DirectHandle<JSFunction> delegate = SimpleCreateFunction(
5041 isolate_, factory->empty_string(),
5042 Builtin::kHandleApiCallAsConstructorDelegate, 0, kDontAdapt);
5043 native_context()->set_call_as_constructor_delegate(*delegate);
5044 }
5045}
5046
5047Handle<JSFunction> Genesis::InstallTypedArray(const char* name,
5048 ElementsKind elements_kind,
5049 InstanceType constructor_type,
5050 int rab_gsab_initial_map_index) {
5051 DirectHandle<JSObject> global(native_context()->global_object(), isolate());
5052
5053 DirectHandle<JSObject> typed_array_prototype =
5054 isolate()->typed_array_prototype();
5055 DirectHandle<JSFunction> typed_array_function =
5056 isolate()->typed_array_function();
5057
5058 Handle<JSFunction> result = InstallFunction(
5059 isolate(), global, name, JS_TYPED_ARRAY_TYPE,
5060 JSTypedArray::kSizeWithEmbedderFields, 0, factory()->the_hole_value(),
5061 Builtin::kTypedArrayConstructor, 3, kDontAdapt);
5062 result->initial_map()->set_elements_kind(elements_kind);
5063
5064 CHECK(JSObject::SetPrototype(isolate(), result, typed_array_function, false,
5065 kDontThrow)
5066 .FromJust());
5067
5068 DirectHandle<Smi> bytes_per_element(
5069 Smi::FromInt(1 << ElementsKindToShiftSize(elements_kind)), isolate());
5070
5071 InstallConstant(isolate(), result, "BYTES_PER_ELEMENT", bytes_per_element);
5072
5073 // TODO(v8:11256, ishell): given the granularity of typed array constructor
5074 // protectors, consider creating only one constructor instance type for all
5075 // typed array constructors.
5076 SetConstructorInstanceType(isolate_, result, constructor_type);
5077
5078 // Setup prototype object.
5079 DCHECK(IsJSObject(result->prototype()));
5080 DirectHandle<JSObject> prototype(Cast<JSObject>(result->prototype()),
5081 isolate());
5082
5083 CHECK(JSObject::SetPrototype(isolate(), prototype, typed_array_prototype,
5084 false, kDontThrow)
5085 .FromJust());
5086
5087 CHECK_NE(prototype->map().ptr(),
5088 isolate_->initial_object_prototype()->map().ptr());
5089 prototype->map()->set_instance_type(JS_TYPED_ARRAY_PROTOTYPE_TYPE);
5090
5091 InstallConstant(isolate(), prototype, "BYTES_PER_ELEMENT", bytes_per_element);
5092
5093 // RAB / GSAB backed TypedArrays don't have separate constructors, but they
5094 // have their own maps. Create the corresponding map here.
5095 DirectHandle<Map> rab_gsab_initial_map =
5096 factory()->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext(
5097 JS_TYPED_ARRAY_TYPE, JSTypedArray::kSizeWithEmbedderFields,
5098 GetCorrespondingRabGsabElementsKind(elements_kind), 0);
5099 rab_gsab_initial_map->SetConstructor(*result);
5100
5101 native_context()->set(rab_gsab_initial_map_index, *rab_gsab_initial_map,
5102 UPDATE_WRITE_BARRIER, kReleaseStore);
5103 Map::SetPrototype(isolate(), rab_gsab_initial_map, prototype);
5104
5105 return result;
5106}

5108void Genesis::InitializeExperimentalGlobal() {
5109#define FEATURE_INITIALIZE_GLOBAL(id, descr) InitializeGlobal_##id();
5110
5111 // Initialize features from more mature to less mature, because less mature
5112 // features may depend on more mature features having been initialized
5113 // already.
5114 HARMONY_SHIPPING(FEATURE_INITIALIZE_GLOBAL)
5115 JAVASCRIPT_SHIPPING_FEATURES(FEATURE_INITIALIZE_GLOBAL)
5116 HARMONY_STAGED(FEATURE_INITIALIZE_GLOBAL)
5117 JAVASCRIPT_STAGED_FEATURES(FEATURE_INITIALIZE_GLOBAL)
5118 HARMONY_INPROGRESS(FEATURE_INITIALIZE_GLOBAL)
5119 JAVASCRIPT_INPROGRESS_FEATURES(FEATURE_INITIALIZE_GLOBAL)
5120#undef FEATURE_INITIALIZE_GLOBAL
5121 InitializeGlobal_regexp_linear_flag();
5122 InitializeGlobal_sharedarraybuffer();
5123}

5125namespace {
5126class TryCallScope {
5127 public:
5128 explicit TryCallScope(Isolate* isolate) : top(isolate->thread_local_top()) {
5129 top->IncrementCallDepth<true>(this);
5130 }
5131 ~TryCallScope() { top->DecrementCallDepth(this); }
5132
5133 private:
5134 friend class i::ThreadLocalTop;
5135 ThreadLocalTop* top;
5136 Address previous_stack_height_;
5137};

5139
5140bool Genesis::CompileExtension(Isolate* isolate, v8::Extension* extension) {
5141 Factory* factory = isolate->factory();
5142 HandleScope scope(isolate);
5143 DirectHandle<SharedFunctionInfo> function_info;
5144
5145 Handle<String> source =
5146 isolate->factory()
5147 ->NewExternalStringFromOneByte(extension->source())
5148 .ToHandleChecked();
5149 DCHECK(source->IsOneByteRepresentation());
5150
5151 // If we can't find the function in the cache, we compile a new
5152 // function and insert it into the cache.
5153 base::Vector<const char> name = base::CStrVector(extension->name());
5154 SourceCodeCache* cache = isolate->bootstrapper()->extensions_cache();
5155 DirectHandle<Context> context(isolate->context(), isolate);
5156 DCHECK(IsNativeContext(*context));
5157
5158 if (!cache->Lookup(isolate, name, &function_info)) {
5159 Handle<String> script_name =
5160 factory->NewStringFromUtf8(name).ToHandleChecked();
5161 ScriptCompiler::CompilationDetails compilation_details;
5162 MaybeDirectHandle<SharedFunctionInfo> maybe_function_info =
5163 Compiler::GetSharedFunctionInfoForScriptWithExtension(
5164 isolate, source, ScriptDetails(script_name), extension,
5165 ScriptCompiler::kNoCompileOptions, EXTENSION_CODE,
5166 &compilation_details);
5167 if (!maybe_function_info.ToHandle(&function_info)) return false;
5168 cache->Add(isolate, name, function_info);
5169 }
5170
5171 // Set up the function context. Conceptually, we should clone the
5172 // function before overwriting the context but since we're in a
5173 // single-threaded environment it is not strictly necessary.
5174 DirectHandle<JSFunction> fun =
5175 Factory::JSFunctionBuilder{isolate, function_info, context}.Build();
5176
5177 // Call function using either the runtime object or the global
5178 // object as the receiver. Provide no parameters.
5179 DirectHandle<Object> receiver = isolate->global_object();
5180 DirectHandle<FixedArray> host_defined_options =
5181 isolate->factory()->empty_fixed_array();
5182 TryCallScope try_call_scope(isolate);
5183 // Blink generally assumes that context creation (where extension compilation
5184 // is part) cannot be interrupted.
5185 PostponeInterruptsScope postpone(isolate);
5186 return !Execution::TryCallScript(isolate, fun, receiver, host_defined_options)
5187 .is_null();
5188}

5190void Genesis::InitializeIteratorFunctions() {
5191 Isolate* isolate = isolate_;
5192 Factory* factory = isolate->factory();
5193 HandleScope scope(isolate);
5194 DirectHandle<NativeContext> native_context = isolate->native_context();
5195 DirectHandle<JSObject> iterator_prototype(
5196 native_context->initial_iterator_prototype(), isolate);
5197
5198 { // -- G e n e r a t o r
5199 PrototypeIterator iter(isolate, native_context->generator_function_map());
5200 DirectHandle<JSObject> generator_function_prototype(
5201 iter.GetCurrent<JSObject>(), isolate);
5202 DirectHandle<JSFunction> generator_function_function = CreateFunction(
5203 isolate, "GeneratorFunction", JS_FUNCTION_TYPE,
5204 JSFunction::kSizeWithPrototype, 0, generator_function_prototype,
5205 Builtin::kGeneratorFunctionConstructor, 1, kDontAdapt);
5206 generator_function_function->set_prototype_or_initial_map(
5207 native_context->generator_function_map(), kReleaseStore);
5208 InstallWithIntrinsicDefaultProto(
5209 isolate, generator_function_function,
5210 Context::GENERATOR_FUNCTION_FUNCTION_INDEX);
5211
5212 JSObject::ForceSetPrototype(isolate, generator_function_function,
5213 isolate->function_function());
5214 JSObject::AddProperty(
5215 isolate, generator_function_prototype, factory->constructor_string(),
5216 generator_function_function,
5217 static_cast<PropertyAttributes>(DONT_ENUM | READ_ONLY));
5218
5219 native_context->generator_function_map()->SetConstructor(
5220 *generator_function_function);
5221 native_context->generator_function_with_name_map()->SetConstructor(
5222 *generator_function_function);
5223 }
5224
5225 { // -- A s y n c G e n e r a t o r
5226 PrototypeIterator iter(isolate,
5227 native_context->async_generator_function_map());
5228 DirectHandle<JSObject> async_generator_function_prototype(
5229 iter.GetCurrent<JSObject>(), isolate);
5230
5231 DirectHandle<JSFunction> async_generator_function_function = CreateFunction(
5232 isolate, "AsyncGeneratorFunction", JS_FUNCTION_TYPE,
5233 JSFunction::kSizeWithPrototype, 0, async_generator_function_prototype,
5234 Builtin::kAsyncGeneratorFunctionConstructor, 1, kDontAdapt);
5235 async_generator_function_function->set_prototype_or_initial_map(
5236 native_context->async_generator_function_map(), kReleaseStore);
5237 InstallWithIntrinsicDefaultProto(
5238 isolate, async_generator_function_function,
5239 Context::ASYNC_GENERATOR_FUNCTION_FUNCTION_INDEX);
5240
5241 JSObject::ForceSetPrototype(isolate, async_generator_function_function,
5242 isolate->function_function());
5243
5244 JSObject::AddProperty(
5245 isolate, async_generator_function_prototype,
5246 factory->constructor_string(), async_generator_function_function,
5247 static_cast<PropertyAttributes>(DONT_ENUM | READ_ONLY));
5248
5249 native_context->async_generator_function_map()->SetConstructor(
5250 *async_generator_function_function);
5251 native_context->async_generator_function_with_name_map()->SetConstructor(
5252 *async_generator_function_function);
5253 }
5254
5255 { // -- S e t I t e r a t o r
5256 // Setup %SetIteratorPrototype%.
5257 DirectHandle<JSObject> prototype =
5258 factory->NewJSObject(isolate->object_function(), AllocationType::kOld);
5259 JSObject::ForceSetPrototype(isolate, prototype, iterator_prototype);
5260
5261 InstallToStringTag(isolate, prototype, factory->SetIterator_string());
5262
5263 // Install the next function on the {prototype}.
5264 InstallFunctionWithBuiltinId(isolate, prototype, "next",
5265 Builtin::kSetIteratorPrototypeNext, 0, kAdapt);
5266 native_context->set_initial_set_iterator_prototype(*prototype);
5267 CHECK_NE(prototype->map().ptr(),
5268 isolate_->initial_object_prototype()->map().ptr());
5269 prototype->map()->set_instance_type(JS_SET_ITERATOR_PROTOTYPE_TYPE);
5270
5271 // Setup SetIterator constructor.
5272 DirectHandle<JSFunction> set_iterator_function =
5273 CreateFunction(isolate, "SetIterator", JS_SET_VALUE_ITERATOR_TYPE,
5274 JSSetIterator::kHeaderSize, 0, prototype,
5275 Builtin::kIllegal, 0, kDontAdapt);
5276 set_iterator_function->shared()->set_native(false);
5277
5278 DirectHandle<Map> set_value_iterator_map(
5279 set_iterator_function->initial_map(), isolate);
5280 native_context->set_set_value_iterator_map(*set_value_iterator_map);
5281
5282 DirectHandle<Map> set_key_value_iterator_map = Map::Copy(
5283 isolate, set_value_iterator_map, "JS_SET_KEY_VALUE_ITERATOR_TYPE");
5284 set_key_value_iterator_map->set_instance_type(
5285 JS_SET_KEY_VALUE_ITERATOR_TYPE);
5286 native_context->set_set_key_value_iterator_map(*set_key_value_iterator_map);
5287 }
5288
5289 { // -- M a p I t e r a t o r
5290 // Setup %MapIteratorPrototype%.
5291 DirectHandle<JSObject> prototype =
5292 factory->NewJSObject(isolate->object_function(), AllocationType::kOld);
5293 JSObject::ForceSetPrototype(isolate, prototype, iterator_prototype);
5294
5295 InstallToStringTag(isolate, prototype, factory->MapIterator_string());
5296
5297 // Install the next function on the {prototype}.
5298 InstallFunctionWithBuiltinId(isolate, prototype, "next",
5299 Builtin::kMapIteratorPrototypeNext, 0, kAdapt);
5300 native_context->set_initial_map_iterator_prototype(*prototype);
5301 CHECK_NE(prototype->map().ptr(),
5302 isolate_->initial_object_prototype()->map().ptr());
5303 prototype->map()->set_instance_type(JS_MAP_ITERATOR_PROTOTYPE_TYPE);
5304
5305 // Setup MapIterator constructor.
5306 DirectHandle<JSFunction> map_iterator_function =
5307 CreateFunction(isolate, "MapIterator", JS_MAP_KEY_ITERATOR_TYPE,
5308 JSMapIterator::kHeaderSize, 0, prototype,
5309 Builtin::kIllegal, 0, kDontAdapt);
5310 map_iterator_function->shared()->set_native(false);
5311
5312 DirectHandle<Map> map_key_iterator_map(map_iterator_function->initial_map(),
5313 isolate);
5314 native_context->set_map_key_iterator_map(*map_key_iterator_map);
5315
5316 DirectHandle<Map> map_key_value_iterator_map = Map::Copy(
5317 isolate, map_key_iterator_map, "JS_MAP_KEY_VALUE_ITERATOR_TYPE");
5318 map_key_value_iterator_map->set_instance_type(
5319 JS_MAP_KEY_VALUE_ITERATOR_TYPE);
5320 native_context->set_map_key_value_iterator_map(*map_key_value_iterator_map);
5321
5322 DirectHandle<Map> map_value_iterator_map =
5323 Map::Copy(isolate, map_key_iterator_map, "JS_MAP_VALUE_ITERATOR_TYPE");
5324 map_value_iterator_map->set_instance_type(JS_MAP_VALUE_ITERATOR_TYPE);
5325 native_context->set_map_value_iterator_map(*map_value_iterator_map);
5326 }
5327
5328 { // -- A s y n c F u n c t i o n
5329 // Builtin functions for AsyncFunction.
5330 PrototypeIterator iter(isolate, native_context->async_function_map());
5331 DirectHandle<JSObject> async_function_prototype(iter.GetCurrent<JSObject>(),
5332 isolate);
5333
5334 DirectHandle<JSFunction> async_function_constructor = CreateFunction(
5335 isolate, "AsyncFunction", JS_FUNCTION_TYPE,
5336 JSFunction::kSizeWithPrototype, 0, async_function_prototype,
5337 Builtin::kAsyncFunctionConstructor, 1, kDontAdapt);
5338 async_function_constructor->set_prototype_or_initial_map(
5339 native_context->async_function_map(), kReleaseStore);
5340 InstallWithIntrinsicDefaultProto(isolate, async_function_constructor,
5341 Context::ASYNC_FUNCTION_FUNCTION_INDEX);
5342
5343 native_context->set_async_function_constructor(*async_function_constructor);
5344 JSObject::ForceSetPrototype(isolate, async_function_constructor,
5345 isolate->function_function());
5346
5347 JSObject::AddProperty(
5348 isolate, async_function_prototype, factory->constructor_string(),
5349 async_function_constructor,
5350 static_cast<PropertyAttributes>(DONT_ENUM | READ_ONLY));
5351
5352 // Async functions don't have a prototype, but they use generator objects
5353 // under the hood to model the suspend/resume (in await). Instead of using
5354 // the "prototype" / initial_map machinery (like for (async) generators),
5355 // there's one global (per native context) map here that is used for the
5356 // async function generator objects. These objects never escape to user
5357 // JavaScript anyways.
5358 DirectHandle<Map> async_function_object_map =
5359 factory->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext(
5360 JS_ASYNC_FUNCTION_OBJECT_TYPE, JSAsyncFunctionObject::kHeaderSize);
5361 native_context->set_async_function_object_map(*async_function_object_map);
5362
5363 isolate_->async_function_map()->SetConstructor(*async_function_constructor);
5364 isolate_->async_function_with_name_map()->SetConstructor(
5365 *async_function_constructor);
5366 }
5367}
5368
5369void Genesis::InitializeCallSiteBuiltins() {
5370 Factory* factory = isolate()->factory();
5371 HandleScope scope(isolate());
5372 // -- C a l l S i t e
5373 // Builtin functions for CallSite.
5374
5375 // CallSites are a special case; the constructor is for our private use
5376 // only, therefore we set it up as a builtin that throws. Internally, we use
5377 // CallSiteUtils::Construct to create CallSite objects.
5378
5379 DirectHandle<JSFunction> callsite_fun = CreateFunction(
5380 isolate(), "CallSite", JS_OBJECT_TYPE, JSObject::kHeaderSize, 0,
5381 factory->the_hole_value(), Builtin::kUnsupportedThrower, 0, kDontAdapt);
5382 isolate()->native_context()->set_callsite_function(*callsite_fun);
5383
5384 // Setup CallSite.prototype.
5385 DirectHandle<JSObject> prototype(
5386 Cast<JSObject>(callsite_fun->instance_prototype()), isolate());
5387
5388 struct FunctionInfo {
5389 const char* name;
5390 Builtin id;
5391 };
5392
5393 FunctionInfo infos[] = {
5394 {"getColumnNumber", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetColumnNumber},
5395 {"getEnclosingColumnNumber",
5396 Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetEnclosingColumnNumber},
5397 {"getEnclosingLineNumber",
5398 Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetEnclosingLineNumber},
5399 {"getEvalOrigin", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetEvalOrigin},
5400 {"getFileName", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetFileName},
5401 {"getFunction", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetFunction},
5402 {"getFunctionName", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetFunctionName},
5403 {"getLineNumber", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetLineNumber},
5404 {"getMethodName", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetMethodName},
5405 {"getPosition", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetPosition},
5406 {"getPromiseIndex", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetPromiseIndex},
5407 {"getScriptNameOrSourceURL",
5408 Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetScriptNameOrSourceURL},
5409 {"getScriptHash", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetScriptHash},
5410 {"getThis", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetThis},
5411 {"getTypeName", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeGetTypeName},
5412 {"isAsync", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeIsAsync},
5413 {"isConstructor", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeIsConstructor},
5414 {"isEval", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeIsEval},
5415 {"isNative", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeIsNative},
5416 {"isPromiseAll", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeIsPromiseAll},
5417 {"isToplevel", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeIsToplevel},
5418 {"toString", Builtin::kCallSitePrototypeToString}};
5419
5420 PropertyAttributes attrs =
5421 static_cast<PropertyAttributes>(DONT_ENUM | DONT_DELETE | READ_ONLY);
5422
5423 for (const FunctionInfo& info : infos) {
5424 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), prototype, info.name, info.id, 0, kAdapt,
5425 attrs);
5426 }
5427}

5458 kDontAdapt, NONE);

5460 kDontAdapt, NONE);

5466 kDontAdapt, NONE);

5468 kDontAdapt, NONE);

5470 kDontAdapt, NONE);

5474 kDontAdapt, NONE);

5476 kDontAdapt, NONE);

5521void Genesis::InitializeGlobal_harmony_iterator_helpers() {
5522 if (!v8_flags.harmony_iterator_helpers) return;
5523
5524 // --- Iterator
5525 DirectHandle<JSGlobalObject> global(native_context()->global_object(),
5526 isolate());
5527 DirectHandle<JSObject> iterator_prototype(
5528 native_context()->initial_iterator_prototype(), isolate());
5529 DirectHandle<JSFunction> iterator_function = InstallFunction(
5530 isolate(), global, "Iterator", JS_OBJECT_TYPE, JSObject::kHeaderSize, 0,
5531 iterator_prototype, Builtin::kIteratorConstructor, 0, kAdapt);
5532 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_function, "from",
5533 Builtin::kIteratorFrom, 1, kAdapt);
5534 InstallWithIntrinsicDefaultProto(isolate(), iterator_function,
5535 Context::ITERATOR_FUNCTION_INDEX);
5536
5537 // --- %WrapForValidIteratorPrototype%
5538 DirectHandle<JSObject> wrap_for_valid_iterator_prototype =
5539 factory()->NewJSObject(isolate()->object_function(),
5540 AllocationType::kOld);
5541 JSObject::ForceSetPrototype(isolate(), wrap_for_valid_iterator_prototype,
5542 iterator_prototype);
5543 JSObject::AddProperty(isolate(), iterator_prototype,
5544 factory()->constructor_string(), iterator_function,
5545 DONT_ENUM);
5546 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), wrap_for_valid_iterator_prototype, "next",
5547 Builtin::kWrapForValidIteratorPrototypeNext, 0, kAdapt);
5548 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), wrap_for_valid_iterator_prototype, "return",
5549 Builtin::kWrapForValidIteratorPrototypeReturn, 0,
5550 kAdapt);
5551 DirectHandle<Map> valid_iterator_wrapper_map =
5552 factory()->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext(
5553 JS_VALID_ITERATOR_WRAPPER_TYPE, JSValidIteratorWrapper::kHeaderSize,
5554 TERMINAL_FAST_ELEMENTS_KIND, 0);
5555 Map::SetPrototype(isolate(), valid_iterator_wrapper_map,
5556 wrap_for_valid_iterator_prototype);
5557 valid_iterator_wrapper_map->SetConstructor(*iterator_function);
5558 native_context()->set_valid_iterator_wrapper_map(*valid_iterator_wrapper_map);
5559 LOG(isolate(), MapDetails(*valid_iterator_wrapper_map));
5560
5561 // --- %IteratorHelperPrototype%
5562 DirectHandle<JSObject> iterator_helper_prototype = factory()->NewJSObject(
5563 isolate()->object_function(), AllocationType::kOld);
5564 JSObject::ForceSetPrototype(isolate(), iterator_helper_prototype,
5565 iterator_prototype);
5566 InstallToStringTag(isolate(), iterator_helper_prototype, "Iterator Helper");
5567 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_helper_prototype, "next",
5568 Builtin::kIteratorHelperPrototypeNext, 0, kAdapt);
5569 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_helper_prototype, "return",
5570 Builtin::kIteratorHelperPrototypeReturn, 0, kAdapt);
5571 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_prototype, "reduce",
5572 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeReduce, 1, kDontAdapt);
5573 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_prototype, "toArray",
5574 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeToArray, 0, kAdapt);
5575 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_prototype, "forEach",
5576 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeForEach, 1, kAdapt);
5577 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_prototype, "some",
5578 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeSome, 1, kAdapt);
5579 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_prototype, "every",
5580 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeEvery, 1, kAdapt);
5581 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_prototype, "find",
5582 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeFind, 1, kAdapt);
5583
5584 // https://github.com/tc39/proposal-iterator-helpers/pull/287
5585 SimpleInstallGetterSetter(isolate(), iterator_prototype,
5586 isolate()->factory()->to_string_tag_symbol(),
5587 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeGetToStringTag,
5588 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeSetToStringTag);
5589
5590 SimpleInstallGetterSetter(isolate(), iterator_prototype,
5591 isolate()->factory()->constructor_string(),
5592 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeGetConstructor,
5593 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeSetConstructor);
5594
5595 // --- Helper maps
5596#define INSTALL_ITERATOR_HELPER(lowercase_name, Capitalized_name, \
5597 ALL_CAPS_NAME, argc) \
5598 { \
5599 DirectHandle<Map> map = factory()->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext( \
5600 JS_ITERATOR_##ALL_CAPS_NAME##_HELPER_TYPE, \
5601 JSIterator##Capitalized_name##Helper::kHeaderSize, \
5602 TERMINAL_FAST_ELEMENTS_KIND, 0); \
5603 Map::SetPrototype(isolate(), map, iterator_helper_prototype); \
5604 map->SetConstructor(*iterator_function); \
5605 native_context()->set_iterator_##lowercase_name##_helper_map(*map); \
5606 LOG(isolate(), MapDetails(*map)); \
5607 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), iterator_prototype, #lowercase_name, \
5608 Builtin::kIteratorPrototype##Capitalized_name, argc, \
5609 kAdapt); \
5610 }
5611
5612#define ITERATOR_HELPERS(V) \
5613 V(map, Map, MAP, 1) \
5614 V(filter, Filter, FILTER, 1) \
5615 V(take, Take, TAKE, 1) \
5616 V(drop, Drop, DROP, 1) \
5617 V(flatMap, FlatMap, FLAT_MAP, 1)
5618
5619 ITERATOR_HELPERS(INSTALL_ITERATOR_HELPER)
5620
5621#undef INSTALL_ITERATOR_HELPER
5622#undef ITERATOR_HELPERS
5623}

5677void Genesis::InitializeGlobal_harmony_shadow_realm() {
5678 if (!v8_flags.harmony_shadow_realm) return;
5679 Factory* factory = isolate()->factory();
5680 // -- S h a d o w R e a l m
5681 // #sec-shadowrealm-objects
5682 DirectHandle<JSGlobalObject> global(native_context()->global_object(),
5683 isolate());
5684 DirectHandle<JSFunction> shadow_realm_fun =
5685 InstallFunction(isolate_, global, "ShadowRealm", JS_SHADOW_REALM_TYPE,
5686 JSShadowRealm::kHeaderSize, 0, factory->the_hole_value(),
5687 Builtin::kShadowRealmConstructor, 0, kDontAdapt);
5688
5689 // Setup %ShadowRealmPrototype%.
5690 DirectHandle<JSObject> prototype(
5691 Cast<JSObject>(shadow_realm_fun->instance_prototype()), isolate());
5692
5693 InstallToStringTag(isolate_, prototype, factory->ShadowRealm_string());
5694
5695 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate_, prototype, "evaluate",
5696 Builtin::kShadowRealmPrototypeEvaluate, 1, kAdapt);
5697 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate_, prototype, "importValue",
5698 Builtin::kShadowRealmPrototypeImportValue, 2, kAdapt);
5699
5700 { // --- W r a p p e d F u n c t i o n
5701 DirectHandle<Map> map = factory->NewContextfulMapForCurrentContext(
5702 JS_WRAPPED_FUNCTION_TYPE, JSWrappedFunction::kHeaderSize,
5703 TERMINAL_FAST_ELEMENTS_KIND, 0);
5704 map->SetConstructor(native_context()->object_function());
5705 map->set_is_callable(true);
5706 DirectHandle<JSObject> empty_function(
5707 native_context()->function_prototype(), isolate());
5708 Map::SetPrototype(isolate(), map, empty_function);
5709
5710 PropertyAttributes roc_attribs =
5711 static_cast<PropertyAttributes>(DONT_ENUM | READ_ONLY);
5712 Map::EnsureDescriptorSlack(isolate_, map, 2);
5713 { // length
5714 static_assert(
5715 JSFunctionOrBoundFunctionOrWrappedFunction::kLengthDescriptorIndex ==
5716 0);
5717 Descriptor d = Descriptor::AccessorConstant(
5718 factory->length_string(), factory->wrapped_function_length_accessor(),
5719 roc_attribs);
5720 map->AppendDescriptor(isolate(), &d);
5721 }
5722
5723 { // name
5724 static_assert(
5725 JSFunctionOrBoundFunctionOrWrappedFunction::kNameDescriptorIndex ==
5726 1);
5727 Descriptor d = Descriptor::AccessorConstant(
5728 factory->name_string(), factory->wrapped_function_name_accessor(),
5729 roc_attribs);
5730 map->AppendDescriptor(isolate(), &d);
5731 }
5732
5733 native_context()->set_wrapped_function_map(*map);
5734 }
5735
5736 // Internal steps of ShadowRealmImportValue
5737 {
5738 DirectHandle<JSFunction> shadow_realm_import_value_rejected =
5739 SimpleCreateFunction(isolate(), factory->empty_string(),
5740 Builtin::kShadowRealmImportValueRejected, 1,
5741 kAdapt);
5742 shadow_realm_import_value_rejected->shared()->set_native(false);
5743 native_context()->set_shadow_realm_import_value_rejected(
5744 *shadow_realm_import_value_rejected);
5745 }
5746}

5921 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), async_disposable_stack_prototype, "adopt",
5922 Builtin::kAsyncDisposableStackPrototypeAdopt, 2,
5923 kAdapt);
5924 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), async_disposable_stack_prototype, "defer",
5925 Builtin::kAsyncDisposableStackPrototypeDefer, 1,
5926 kAdapt);
5927 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), async_disposable_stack_prototype, "move",
5928 Builtin::kAsyncDisposableStackPrototypeMove, 0, kAdapt);
5929
5930 InstallToStringTag(isolate(), async_disposable_stack_prototype,
5931 "AsyncDisposableStack");
5932 SimpleInstallGetter(
5933 isolate(), async_disposable_stack_prototype, factory->disposed_string(),
5934 Builtin::kAsyncDisposableStackPrototypeGetDisposed, kAdapt);
5935
5936 // Add symbols to iterator prototypes
5937 DirectHandle<JSObject> iterator_prototype(
5938 native_context()->initial_iterator_prototype(), isolate());
5939 InstallFunctionAtSymbol(isolate(), iterator_prototype,
5940 factory->dispose_symbol(), "[Symbol.dispose]",
5941 Builtin::kIteratorPrototypeDispose, 0, kAdapt);
5942
5943 DirectHandle<JSObject> async_iterator_prototype(
5944 native_context()->initial_async_iterator_prototype(), isolate());
5945 InstallFunctionAtSymbol(
5946 isolate(), async_iterator_prototype, factory->async_dispose_symbol(),
5947 "[Symbol.asyncDispose]", Builtin::kAsyncIteratorPrototypeAsyncDispose, 0,
5948 kAdapt);
5949}

5951void Genesis::InitializeGlobal_js_float16array() {
5952 if (!v8_flags.js_float16array) return;
5953
5954 DirectHandle<JSGlobalObject> global(native_context()->global_object(),
5955 isolate());
5956 DirectHandle<JSObject> math = Cast<JSObject>(
5957 JSReceiver::GetProperty(isolate(), global, "Math").ToHandleChecked());
5958
5959 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate_, math, "f16round", Builtin::kMathF16round, 1,
5960 kAdapt);
5961
5962 DirectHandle<JSObject> dataview_prototype(
5963 Cast<JSObject>(native_context()->data_view_fun()->instance_prototype()),
5964 isolate());
5965
5966 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate_, dataview_prototype, "getFloat16",
5967 Builtin::kDataViewPrototypeGetFloat16, 1, kDontAdapt);
5968 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate_, dataview_prototype, "setFloat16",
5969 Builtin::kDataViewPrototypeSetFloat16, 2, kDontAdapt);
5970
5971 DirectHandle<JSFunction> fun = InstallTypedArray(
5972 "Float16Array", FLOAT16_ELEMENTS, FLOAT16_TYPED_ARRAY_CONSTRUCTOR_TYPE,
5973 Context::RAB_GSAB_FLOAT16_ARRAY_MAP_INDEX);
5974
5975 InstallWithIntrinsicDefaultProto(isolate_, fun,
5976 Context::FLOAT16_ARRAY_FUN_INDEX);
5977}

5979void Genesis::InitializeGlobal_js_source_phase_imports() {
5980 if (!v8_flags.js_source_phase_imports) return;
5981 Factory* factory = isolate()->factory();
5982 // -- %AbstractModuleSource%
5983 // #sec-%abstractmodulesource%
5984 // https://tc39.es/proposal-source-phase-imports/#sec-%abstractmodulesource%
5985 DirectHandle<JSFunction> abstract_module_source_fun =
5986 CreateFunction(isolate_, "AbstractModuleSource", JS_OBJECT_TYPE,
5987 JSObject::kHeaderSize, 0, factory->the_hole_value(),
5988 Builtin::kIllegalInvocationThrower, 0, kDontAdapt);
5989

5991 *abstract_module_source_fun);
5992
5993 // Setup %AbstractModuleSourcePrototype%.
5994 DirectHandle<JSObject> abstract_module_source_prototype(
5995 Cast<JSObject>(abstract_module_source_fun->instance_prototype()),
5996 isolate());
5997 native_context()->set_abstract_module_source_prototype(
5998 *abstract_module_source_prototype);
5999
6000 SimpleInstallGetter(isolate(), abstract_module_source_prototype,
6001 isolate()->factory()->to_string_tag_symbol(),
6002 Builtin::kAbstractModuleSourceToStringTag, kAdapt);
6003}

6020void Genesis::InitializeGlobal_harmony_temporal() {
6021 if (!v8_flags.harmony_temporal) return;
6022
6023 // The Temporal object is set up lazily upon first access.
6024 {
6025 Handle<JSGlobalObject> global(native_context()->global_object(), isolate());
6026 DirectHandle<String> name = factory()->InternalizeUtf8String("Temporal");
6027 DirectHandle<AccessorInfo> accessor = Accessors::MakeAccessor(
6028 isolate(), name, LazyInitializeGlobalThisTemporal, nullptr);
6029 accessor->set_replace_on_access(true);
6030 JSObject::SetAccessor(global, name, accessor, DONT_ENUM).Check();
6031 }
6032
6033 // Likewise Date.toTemporalInstant.
6034 {
6035 DirectHandle<JSFunction> date_func(native_context()->date_function(),
6036 isolate());
6037 Handle<JSObject> date_prototype(
6038 Cast<JSObject>(date_func->instance_prototype()), isolate());
6039 DirectHandle<String> name =
6040 factory()->InternalizeUtf8String("toTemporalInstant");
6041 DirectHandle<AccessorInfo> accessor = Accessors::MakeAccessor(
6042 isolate(), name, LazyInitializeDateToTemporalInstant, nullptr);
6043 accessor->set_replace_on_access(true);
6044 JSObject::SetAccessor(date_prototype, name, accessor, DONT_ENUM).Check();
6045 }
6046}
6047
6048Handle<JSFunction> Genesis::CreateArrayBuffer(
6049 DirectHandle<String> name, ArrayBufferKind array_buffer_kind) {
6050 // Create the %ArrayBufferPrototype%
6051 // Setup the {prototype} with the given {name} for @@toStringTag.
6052 DirectHandle<JSObject> prototype = factory()->NewJSObject(
6053 isolate()->object_function(), AllocationType::kOld);
6054 InstallToStringTag(isolate(), prototype, name);
6055
6056 // Allocate the constructor with the given {prototype}.
6057 Handle<JSFunction> array_buffer_fun =
6058 CreateFunction(isolate(), name, JS_ARRAY_BUFFER_TYPE,
6059 JSArrayBuffer::kSizeWithEmbedderFields, 0, prototype,
6060 Builtin::kArrayBufferConstructor, 1, kAdapt);
6061
6062 // Install the "constructor" property on the {prototype}.
6063 JSObject::AddProperty(isolate(), prototype, factory()->constructor_string(),
6064 array_buffer_fun, DONT_ENUM);
6065
6066 switch (array_buffer_kind) {
6067 case ARRAY_BUFFER:
6068 InstallFunctionWithBuiltinId(isolate(), array_buffer_fun, "isView",
6069 Builtin::kArrayBufferIsView, 1, kAdapt);
6070
6071 // Install the "byteLength" getter on the {prototype}.
6072 SimpleInstallGetter(isolate(), prototype, factory()->byte_length_string(),
6073 Builtin::kArrayBufferPrototypeGetByteLength, kAdapt);
6074 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), prototype, "slice",
6075 Builtin::kArrayBufferPrototypeSlice, 2, kAdapt);
6076 break;
6077
6078 case SHARED_ARRAY_BUFFER:
6079 // Install the "byteLength" getter on the {prototype}.
6080 SimpleInstallGetter(isolate(), prototype, factory()->byte_length_string(),
6081 Builtin::kSharedArrayBufferPrototypeGetByteLength,
6082 kDontAdapt);
6083 SimpleInstallFunction(isolate(), prototype, "slice",
6084 Builtin::kSharedArrayBufferPrototypeSlice, 2,
6085 kAdapt);
6086 break;
6087 }
6088
6089 return array_buffer_fun;
6090}
